data.description: Excellent E Memphis location, Super clean!! Wood floors, large tiles in kitchen One level living, immaculate and ready for you to move in. Refrigerator, washing machine and dryer stay. Renovated ranch home. 4 bed/2 bath. Large kitchen, plenty of cabinets and storage! 2 pantries Open concept layout with 2 separate living areas, a seamless flow for entertaining & comfortable living. Veterans & Active Duty military: this home has an assumable 3% interest VA loan. 2 off street parking spaces.
